Shocking surveillance video from the day before Robyn Gardner disappeared in Aruba shows her being led by the prime suspect to the stretch of beach from which she would vanish a day later.

Fresh evidence shows the pair clearly visiting the same area, in what experts believe could have been a test run before she was murdered.

Giordano, 50, is the only suspect being questioned in relation to the
disappearance of Gardner, 35, who has been missing since August 2. The older man, who she is thought to have met on an online swingers website, is being held in custody for 60 days, but police need
more evidence to charge him with murder.

